{"tid":1447124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全部同我入撚曬黎","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:13.000Z","uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"655215c614e39c2400dabc26b3d267b90c3dc028","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係鬼，亦唔係分化撚<br />\n我唔係鬼，亦唔係分化撚<br />\n我唔係鬼，亦唔係分化撚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n屌那星，今日係尖沙咀，前線準備打，後面叫走，仲叫人跑？<br />\n你可以叫人走，但係現場不斷叫急步1212，就有班仆街，叫人跑起身<br />\n如果人踩人發生左，個傷亡仲大過比警察拉，比速龍打<br />\n親眼見有女仔跌親，兩隻腳損曬 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好急 唔好停</strong></span></span></span><br />\n如果身邊有人不斷叫跑，唔該叫停佢把口，大叫1212<br />\n<br />\n今日其實大家都睇到換左玩法<br />\n臥底早已見怪不怪，但係呢種新型臥底係第一次<br />\n不過絕對係有得認，不過唔好以上次既標誌做目標<br />\n但係有一樣也可能可以做辨認，我相信佢地點都係需要耳機做溝通<br />\n無論係骨傳導耳機，有線無線，只有現場見到戴耳機既就先大叫有狗，圍左條友先，再審問<br />\n寧殺錯無放過，作為臥底我相信佢地預左比人打，所以證據確鑿就手起刀落打落啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*本人唔鼓吹對人左出任何暴力行為（犬隻除外）<br />\n<br />\n下次有人不斷叫走，跑，但如果前線真係走唔切就試下叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【融左佢】</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">*記住唔好跑*</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*絕對唔好跑*</span></span></strong></span><br />\n若言前線決定<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">作出反擊</span></span>，請叫停，並向前聲援前線作出反擊<br />\n<br />\n612後警隊變成犬隻，721後犬隻不如，唔好害怕你落手會傷到人<br />\n人絕對唔會同你計較，只有犬隻不如既生物會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>寧冤枉人，不放棄義士<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"20ffee03f197f077536c202c885eb106ec181c68","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a4364a984aa9a4a058a034b2c6f0c4db6b85e14","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0533721229573767e64f8c58eb65288cf6418891","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"9530c8b1a6ac2ba3c0b1229c2b554d4057434206","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"f0bfe9af7c3e88a924b0807e932649f74b6d5761","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c75ec5196a172565d2ddf3cdb59222e2e048981d","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"dd989d991bd579b234b2ce23aa6e64ac7fcd9e06","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a346624103bccc275a7d82292e7b9d59cc92edb1","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"211fa628d99a3de4c64e685d6df1aff711c1aa2c","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6cbda61a1076d27398395054e8c5e595ac636960","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"ba0e2ccf362feb0d55f8dafe1f5b394b5ecbf07a","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"da62acfed5f42cbb5482de6e37836de7bd637db4","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a3f0ea771db1be4a1cf7deccd673f628b81fc18b","tid":1447124,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB